snippets.snippet: Tokyo (/ ˈ t oʊ k i ˌ oʊ /; Japanese: 東京, Tōkyō ), officially Tokyo Metropolis (東京都, Tōkyō-to), is the capital of Japan and the most populous of the country's 47 prefectures. Located at the head of Tokyo Bay, the prefecture forms part of the Kantō region on the central Pacific coast of Japan's main island, Honshu.
